            <ul class="rulelist">
              <li class="rulelist">Participating teams will have to prepare a report of their Presentation with required graphic details, in less than 1000 words, and mail it to the address of <font color="#fcffc1">pantheon17bitm@gmail.com</font> before the 10<sup>th</sup> of October.</li>
