              <li class="rulelist">The teams will be given 15 minutes to present their research paper with a supplementary PowerPoint presentation.</li>
              <li class="rulelist">The selected teams have to submit at least five hard copies of their research to the esteemed panel who will be scrutinizing their research.</li>
              <li class="rulelist">There will be an additional viva session of every team at the end of their presentations.</li>
